    <string name="rules_text">
        Welcome to Imaginarium!
        \n\nNow we want to tell you the rules of the game.
        \n\nThe game begins with choosing the number of players: 3-6 and entering their names. You can use the microphone for the task name voice.
        \n\nIn the next window you have to choose a game level in which you and your team will play.
        \n\nIn the upper right corner, you can select the game mode: time for guessing one word, total game time, number of rounds (1 round = number of words at which each player will guess 1 word)
        \n\nIn case when the player has guessed the word - 1 point is given to the player who made the word and the one who guessed the word.
        \n\nThe game ends when the players have played the selected number of rounds or the total game time is over.
       </string>


